class.name: ClashResults
class.abstract: A collection of all ClashResult objects currently managed by the application.

method.name: AddFromXML
method.abstract: Creates a ClashResult object from a XML file and adds it to the ClashResults collection.

method.name: Item
method.abstract: Returns a ClashResult object using its index or its name from the ClashResults collection.

method.name: Remove
method.abstract: Removes a ClashResult object from the ClashResults collection.

class.name: Clashes
class.abstract: A collection of all Clash objects currently managed by the application.

method.name: Add
method.abstract: Creates a Clash object which takes all products into account and adds it to the Clashes collection.

method.name: AddFromSel
method.abstract: Creates a Clash object which takes all products in the selection into account and adds it to the Clashes collection.

method.name: Item
method.abstract: Returns a Clash object using its index or its name from the Clashes collection.

method.name: Remove
method.abstract: Removes a Clash object from the Clashes collection.

method.name: GetFirstPointCoordinates
method.abstract: Retrieves the coordinates of the point on the first product which realizes the penetration or minimum distance.

method.name: GetSecondPointCoordinates
method.abstract: Retrieves the coordinates of the point on the second product which realizes the penetration or minimum distance.

method.name: Comment
method.abstract: Returns or sets a comment on the conflict.

method.name: ComparisonInfo
method.abstract: Returns the information on the comparison between the conflict and the previous one.

method.name: FirstProduct
method.abstract: Returns the first product involved in the conflict.

method.name: SecondProduct
method.abstract: Returns the second product involved in the conflict.

method.name: Status
method.abstract: Returns or sets the status of the conflict.

method.name: Type
method.abstract: Returns the type of the conflict.

method.name: Value
method.abstract: Returns the conflict value.

class.name: Conflicts
class.abstract: A collection of all Conflict objects currently detected by a Clash object.

method.name: Item
method.abstract: Returns a Conflict object using its index from the Conflicts collection.

method.name: Compute
method.abstract: Computes the distance.

method.name: GetFirstPointCoordinates
method.abstract: Retrieves the coordinates of the point belonging to the first product, which realizes the distance.

method.name: GetSecondPointCoordinates
method.abstract: Retrieves the coordinates of the point belonging to the second product, which realizes the distance.

method.name: Accuracy
method.abstract: Returns or sets the accuracy value for the computation.

method.name: AnnotatedViews
method.abstract: Returns the AnnotatedViews collection of the distance.

method.name: ComputationType
method.abstract: Returns or sets the computation type for the computation.

method.name: FirstGroup
method.abstract: Returns or sets the first group used by the computation.

method.name: FirstProduct
method.abstract: Returns the product belonging to the first group that realizes the minimum distance.

method.name: IsDefined
method.abstract: Returns a diagnosis on the distance.

method.name: Marker3Ds
method.abstract: Returns the Marker3Ds collection of the distance.

method.name: MaximumDistance
method.abstract: Returns or sets the maximum distance value for the computation (valid only for band analysis).

method.name: MeasureType
method.abstract: Returns or sets the type of distance that will be calculated.

method.name: MinimumDistance
method.abstract: Returns or sets the minimum distance value for the computation (valid only for band analysis).

method.name: SecondGroup
method.abstract: Returns or sets the second group used by the computation.

method.name: SecondProduct
method.abstract: Returns the product belonging to the second group that realizes the minimum distance.

method.name: Value
method.abstract: Returns the distance value.

class.name: Distances
class.abstract: A collection of all Distance objects currently managed by the application.

method.name: Add
method.abstract: Creates a Distance object which takes all products of the document into account and adds it to the Distances collection.

method.name: AddFromSel
method.abstract: Creates a Distance object which takes all products in the selection into account and adds it to the Distances collection.

method.name: Item
method.abstract: Returns a Distance object using its index or its name from the Distances collection.

method.name: Remove
method.abstract: Removes a Distance object from the Distances collection.

method.abstract: Returns or sets the density for the computation.

method.name: Mass
method.abstract: Returns the mass.

class.name: Measurable
class.abstract: The interface to access a CATIAMeasurable Get measurements on the object.

method.name: GetAngleBetween
method.abstract: Compute the angle between the CATIAMeasurable and another.

method.abstract: Retrieves the axis vector of the cylinder or a cone.

method.name: GetAxisSystem
method.abstract: Retrieves the information of the axis system.

method.name: GetCOG
method.abstract: Retrieves the position of the center of gravity of a surface and volume .

method.name: GetCenter
method.abstract: Retrieves the position of the center of a circle or sphere.

method.name: GetDirection
method.abstract: Retrieves the direction of the line.

method.name: GetMinimumDistance
method.abstract: Compute the minimum distance between the CATIAMeasurable and another.

method.name: GetMinimumDistancePoints
method.abstract: Compute the points corresponding to the minimum distance between the two references.

method.name: GetPlane
method.abstract: Retrieves informations of the plane.

method.name: GetPoint
method.abstract: Retrieves the position of the point.

method.name: GetPointsOnAxis
method.abstract: Retrieves the the characteristic points of the axis with respect of the size of the revolution object.

method.name: GetPointsOnCurve
method.abstract: Retrieves the the characteristic points of the curve : the start point, the middle point and the end point.

method.name: Angle
method.abstract: Returns the Angle of a circle or cone.

method.name: Area
method.abstract: Returns the area of the surface or wet area from volume.

method.name: GeometryName
method.abstract: Returns the name of the geometry of the measured object.

method.name: Length
method.abstract: Returns the Length of a curve.

method.name: Perimeter
method.abstract: Returns the perimeter of a surface.

method.name: Radius
method.abstract: Returns the radius of an arc, cylinder or sphere.

method.name: Volume
method.abstract: Returns the volume.
